		<item>
		<title>【Minecraft】Fabricの軽量化MOD「Sodium」、「Canvas Renderer」、「OptiFine」と代替MOD、Sodiumアドオンの紹介</title>
		<link>https://blog.pkom.ml/2022072081/</link>
					<comments>https://blog.pkom.ml/2022072081/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Pitan]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 20 Jul 2022 05:17:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Minecraft]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[ゲーム]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[FabricMC]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[MOD]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://blog.pkom.ml/?p=81</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[目次 軽量化MODSodiumCanvas RendererOptiFine + OptiFabricOptiFineOptiFabricSodiumアドオン、代替MODSodium拡張MOD「Sodium Extra」 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[

  <div id="toc" class="toc tnt-number toc-center tnt-number border-element"><input type="checkbox" class="toc-checkbox" id="toc-checkbox-8" checked><label class="toc-title" for="toc-checkbox-8">目次</label>
    <div class="toc-content">
    <ol class="toc-list open"><li><a href="#toc1" tabindex="0">軽量化MOD</a><ol><li><a href="#toc2" tabindex="0">Sodium</a></li><li><a href="#toc3" tabindex="0">Canvas Renderer</a></li><li><a href="#toc4" tabindex="0">OptiFine + OptiFabric</a><ol><li><a href="#toc5" tabindex="0">OptiFine</a></li><li><a href="#toc6" tabindex="0">OptiFabric</a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li><a href="#toc7" tabindex="0">Sodiumアドオン、代替MOD</a><ol><li><a href="#toc8" tabindex="0">Sodium拡張MOD「Sodium Extra」</a></li><li><a href="#toc9" tabindex="0">シェーダー読み込みMOD「Iris Shaders」</a></li><li><a href="#toc10" tabindex="0">Fabric Rendering APIとの互換性を修正するMOD「Indium」</a></li><li><a href="#toc11" tabindex="0">照明エンジン最適化MOD「Phosphor」</a></li><li><a href="#toc12" tabindex="0">汎用最適化MOD「Lithium」</a></li><li><a href="#toc13" tabindex="0">ビデオ設定を元に戻すMOD「Better Sodium Video Settings Button」</a></li><li><a href="#toc14" tabindex="0">メモリ使用量削減MOD「FerriteCore」</a></li><li><a href="#toc15" tabindex="0">ダイナミックライト「LambDynamicLights」</a></li><li><a href="#toc16" tabindex="0">ズームMOD「Logical Zoom」</a></li><li><a href="#toc17" tabindex="0">テクスチャを接続するMOD「Continuity」</a></li><li><a href="#toc18" tabindex="0">メモリを解放するMOD「MemoryLeakFix」</a></li><li><a href="#toc19" tabindex="0">Sodiumの設定画面を改善するMOD「Reese&#8217;s Sodium Options」</a></li></ol></li></ol>
    </div>
  </div>

<h2><span id="toc1">軽量化MOD</span></h2>



<p>※Sodium、Canvas、OptiFineを併用することはできません。</p>



<h3><span id="toc2">Sodium</span></h3>



<p>マイクラのFPSが数倍高くなる描画処理を最適化するMODです。<br />OptiFineよりSodiumの方が断然良いと私は思います。<br />OptiFineの機能がすべてあるわけでもないので代わりのMOD、アドオンも紹介ていきます。</p>



<a rel="noopener" href="https://modrinth.com/mod/sodium" title="Sodium - Mods - Modrinth" class="blogcard-wrap external-blogcard-wrap a-wrap cf" target="_blank"><div class="blogcard external-blogcard eb-left cf"><div class="blogcard-label external-blogcard-label"><span class="fa"></span></div><figure class="blogcard-thumbnail external-blogcard-thumbnail"><img src="https://s.wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Fmodrinth.com%2Fmod%2Fsodium?w=160&#038;h=90" alt="" class="blogcard-thumb-image external-blogcard-thumb-image" width="160" height="90" /></figure><div class="blogcard-content external-blogcard-content"><div class="blogcard-title external-blogcard-title">Sodium - Mods - Modrinth</div><div class="blogcard-snippet external-blogcard-snippet">Sodium: Modern rendering engine and client-side optimization mod for Minecraft View other minecraft mods on Modrinth today! Modrinth is a new and modern Minecra...</div></div><div class="blogcard-footer external-blogcard-footer cf"><div class="blogcard-site external-blogcard-site"><div class="blogcard-favicon external-blogcard-favicon"><img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://modrinth.com/mod/sodium" alt="" class="blogcard-favicon-image external-blogcard-favicon-image" width="16" height="16" /></div><div class="blogcard-domain external-blogcard-domain">modrinth.com</div></div></div></div></a>



<h3><span id="toc3">Canvas Renderer</span></h3>



<p>パフォーマンスを最大限に発揮させる軽量化MODです。</p>



<a rel="noopener" href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/canvas-renderer" title="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/canvas-renderer" class="blogcard-wrap external-blogcard-wrap a-wrap cf" target="_blank"><div class="blogcard external-blogcard eb-left cf"><div class="blogcard-label external-blogcard-label"><span class="fa"></span></div><figure class="blogcard-thumbnail external-blogcard-thumbnail"><img src="https://s.wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curseforge.com%2Fminecraft%2Fmc-mods%2Fcanvas-renderer?w=160&#038;h=90" alt="" class="blogcard-thumb-image external-blogcard-thumb-image" width="160" height="90" /></figure><div class="blogcard-content external-blogcard-content"><div class="blogcard-title external-blogcard-title">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/canvas-renderer</div><div class="blogcard-snippet external-blogcard-snippet"></div></div><div class="blogcard-footer external-blogcard-footer cf"><div class="blogcard-site external-blogcard-site"><div class="blogcard-favicon external-blogcard-favicon"><img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/canvas-renderer" alt="" class="blogcard-favicon-image external-blogcard-favicon-image" width="16" height="16" /></div><div class="blogcard-domain external-blogcard-domain">www.curseforge.com</div></div></div></div></a>



<h3><span id="toc4">OptiFine + OptiFabric</span></h3>



<p>Fabricでは以下の2つを導入しないとOptiFineが動きません。</p>



<h4><span id="toc5">OptiFine</span></h4>



<p>定番の軽量化MODであるOptiFineです。<br />ちなみに本来は軽量化目的で作られたものではないみたいですね^^;</p>



<a rel="noopener" href="https://optifine.net/downloads" title="OptiFine Downloads" class="blogcard-wrap external-blogcard-wrap a-wrap cf" target="_blank"><div class="blogcard external-blogcard eb-left cf"><div class="blogcard-label external-blogcard-label"><span class="fa"></span></div><figure class="blogcard-thumbnail external-blogcard-thumbnail"><img src="https://s.wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Foptifine.net%2Fdownloads?w=160&#038;h=90" alt="" class="blogcard-thumb-image external-blogcard-thumb-image" width="160" height="90" /></figure><div class="blogcard-content external-blogcard-content"><div class="blogcard-title external-blogcard-title">OptiFine Downloads</div><div class="blogcard-snippet external-blogcard-snippet">OptiFine - Minecraft performance tuning and advanced graphics</div></div><div class="blogcard-footer external-blogcard-footer cf"><div class="blogcard-site external-blogcard-site"><div class="blogcard-favicon external-blogcard-favicon"><img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://optifine.net/downloads" alt="" class="blogcard-favicon-image external-blogcard-favicon-image" width="16" height="16" /></div><div class="blogcard-domain external-blogcard-domain">optifine.net</div></div></div></div></a>



<h4><span id="toc6">OptiFabric</span></h4>



<p>一時期開発停止を公表するなどありましたが、Chocohead氏が引き継いでくださった有志が更新し続けているMODです。</p>



<a rel="noopener" href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/optifabric" title="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/optifabric" class="blogcard-wrap external-blogcard-wrap a-wrap cf" target="_blank"><div class="blogcard external-blogcard eb-left cf"><div class="blogcard-label external-blogcard-label"><span class="fa"></span></div><figure class="blogcard-thumbnail external-blogcard-thumbnail"><img src="https://s.wordpress.com/mshots/v1/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.curseforge.com%2Fminecraft%2Fmc-mods%2Foptifabric?w=160&#038;h=90" alt="" class="blogcard-thumb-image external-blogcard-thumb-image" width="160" height="90" /></figure><div class="blogcard-content external-blogcard-content"><div class="blogcard-title external-blogcard-title">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/optifabric</div><div class="blogcard-snippet external-blogcard-snippet"></div></div><div class="blogcard-footer external-blogcard-footer cf"><div class="blogcard-site external-blogcard-site"><div class="blogcard-favicon external-blogcard-favicon"><img src="https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/optifabric" alt="" class="blogcard-favicon-image external-blogcard-favicon-image" width="16" height="16" /></div><div class="blogcard-domain external-blogcard-domain">www.curseforge.com</div></div></div></div></a>



<h2><span id="toc7">Sodiumアドオン、代替MOD</span></h2>
<h3><span id="toc8">Sodium拡張MOD「Sodium Extra」</span></h3>
<p>Sodiumにはないオプションを追加するSodiumアドオンです。</p>
